item.title: SoftLayer_Hardware_Component_Firmware_Attribute_Type
item.description: SoftLayer_Hardware_Component_Firmware_Attribute_Type Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Hardware_Component_Firmware_Attribute_Type data type defines attribute types for a hardware component model’s firmware. Local description The description for the date that a hardware component attribute type's [[SoftLayer_Hardware_Component_Attribute|Attribute]] contains. Type: string id A hardware component firmware attribute type's Id. Type: integer keyName A hardware component firmware attribute type's unique name. Type: string name A hardware component firmware attribute type's name.
